David S. HASTINGS, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-3407 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 06, 2017

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for writ of certiorari is denied. See Spaulding v. State, 93 So. 3d 473 , 474-475 (Fla. 2d DCA 2012).

SILBERMAN, LUCAS, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
